      • readNullableJSONObject

        @Nullable
public static JSONObject readNullableJSONObject(Parcel in)
        Attempts to read a JSONObject from the given Parcel at its current data position.
        Parameters:
        in - The Parcel to read the JSON object from
        Returns:
        The JSONObject at the parcel's current data position, or null if the parcel doesn't contain valid JSON data or if the JSON object was null.
